{"tid":977690,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"在機場禁區踢毽","createTime":"2019-01-11T11:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T02:07:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5985239dc08d5098166a153b5e5d54414d085c28","tid":977690,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190111/20588108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190111%2F20588108&d=M%2FGs6wTTKW0q7aBMIZmwLy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=972e03e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190111%2F20588108&h=85fa2890\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190111/20588108</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月11日 <br />\n<br />\n在機場禁區踢毽 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190111/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190111%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=e58ec510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壹週刊(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有人在香港機場禁區內拍到一段短片放上網絡，只見幾個大媽在旁若無人踢毽，若非登機閘顯示航班由香港出發，還真的難以置信發生在香港國際機場。<br />\n<br />\n禁區內當然沒有中英文告示禁止乘客踢毽，正如禁區內亦無告示禁止大媽跳大媽舞，以及隨地吐痰、隨地大小便、穿泳衣躺在落地玻璃前曬日光浴，或者拿出自熱火鍋蹲在閘口前開餐&hellip;&hellip;可是，在適當的場合做適當的事，其實是成年人的常識及基本禮貌。即使是去陌生地方，不了解當地習俗或禁忌，只要稍微觀察一下周圍，別人不做的事情你也不做，基本上不會錯。<br />\n<br />\n大媽們最叫人厭惡的不是她們的舞姿、歌藝、行為，而是所有這些行為背後的東西：她們完全漠視其他人感受的絕對自私自利。正常人，只要發現自己的行為令旁人厭惡，對旁人造成滋擾，就會感到不安，然後收斂。但大媽們不然，她們甚至以挑釁他們為樂，你覺得不舒服？我偏偏動作更大一些！我就是要讓你不舒服，你不舒服我就爽！在極權制度下長大的人，無力反抗極權，卻用盡方法欺凌他人，感受凌駕他人意志的邪惡快感。<br />\n<br />\n當香港國際機場禁區變身為大媽們的私家遊樂場而無人阻止，日後，恐怕會有人跳繩、打羽毛球、玩瑜伽、食火鍋&hellip;&hellip;  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【有限創意】萬惡塑膠　合法大麻 (余家強)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n「一國兩制」，其名不正 (古德明)"},{"pid":"576f6164c82d885336538d4754423f6e2cd1ebd4","tid":977690,"uid":37220,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:07:35.000Z","msg":"無咩問題<br />\n又無騷擾到人"},{"pid":"5e57bb77bae4b79b759d45645565a215003ed6ef","tid":977690,"uid":69083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:20:24.000Z","msg":"如果係鬼佬在香港國際機場踢足球會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec41690a9f08aba436c39ed4afcf32c47cd6ab1","tid":977690,"uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5e57bb77bae4b79b759d45645565a215003ed6ef","tid":977690,"uid":69083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:20:24.000Z","msg":"如果係鬼佬在香港國際機場踢足球會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:27:20.000Z","msg":"Nike or Adidas 廣告"},{"pid":"5c92cbfaa8890813cac728f29c4c41030562ce72","tid":977690,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實有咩問題？"},{"pid":"d51717d0a7075da492911e95aab0004f27895b19","tid":977690,"uid":54524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c92cbfaa8890813cac728f29c4c41030562ce72","tid":977690,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實有咩問題？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:11:38.000Z","msg":"問題係人種，唔係行為"},{"pid":"db810af5ee59ad651b60d06e5ae7bd398eced13f","tid":977690,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:58:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ac90f613b0de383ff46c5a0677e1109d15ab2b0","tid":977690,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db810af5ee59ad651b60d06e5ae7bd398eced13f